flowRoot.flowPara: When a shape is selected, the customize shape pop-up appears on it's right side with all the available options this shape has. It is formed by 2 elements: the options nav on the left and the settings area on the right.

Each shape has different options based on the shape you have selected. If you select more than one shape (group) the customize shape pop-up shows only the options these shapes have in common to set them at the same time.
